dc_description_s: Attendance boundaries for high schools in the Chicago Public Schools district for school year 2015-2016. Generally, all students in the applicable middle school grades who live within one of these boundaries may attend the school. To view or use these shapefiles, compression software, such as 7-Zip, and special GIS software, such as Google Earth or ArcGIS, are required.Note: this file has the wrong extension. To extract the shapefile, rename the extension of downloaded file from .kmz to .zip
dc_title_s: High School Attendance Boundaries: Chicago, Illinois, 2015-2016
